<template><div><h1 id="线性支持向量机与软间隔最大化" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#线性支持向量机与软间隔最大化" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 线性支持向量机与软间隔最大化</h1>
<ul>
<li>
<p><RouterLink to="/docs/machine-learning/machine-learning/support-vector-machine/support-vector-machine.html">返回上层目录</RouterLink></p>
