<p><a href="#%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%90%91%E9%87%8F%E6%9C%BA%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%B9%E5%81%B6%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95">线性支持向量机学习的对偶算法</a></p>
</li>
